            <title>Listening Room</title>
            <link>http://localhost:1313/page/listening-room/</link>
            <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 08:02:49 -0500</pubDate>
            <guid>http://localhost:1313/page/listening-room/</guid>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;You have arrived at the Listening Room. Music has a funny way of inhabiting a place. Some albums become companions for a week. Others return every few years like old friends. This room is where I leave them out. Take your time. Flip through the rack. You might leave with a new favorite.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-record-rack&#34;&gt;The Record Rack&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The albums currently keeping me company.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div id=&#34;record-rack&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;rack&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/Listening Room/Albums/anginedepoitrine.jpeg&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
        </item><item>
